ZH: 如果违反规定，他将受到严厉的处罚。
EN: He will face severe punishment if he violates the regulations.

ZH: 这个罪犯将会因犯罪行为而受到处罚。
EN: The criminal will be punished for his criminal actions.

ZH: 这个学生要被处罚，因为他没有按时交作业。
EN: This student will be penalized for not submitting the assignment on time.

ZH: 警察对交通违规者进行了处罚。
EN: The police punished the traffic violators.

ZH: 因盗窃罪，小偷被判处了十年的处罚。
EN: The thief was sentenced to ten years of punishment for the crime of theft.

ZH: 这项政策将对环境破坏者进行处罚。
EN: This policy will punish those who cause environmental damage.

ZH: 这个公司因欺诈被处以高额罚款。
EN: The company was fined heavily for fraud.

ZH: 如果你不遵守规则，你将受到校规的处罚。
EN: If you don't follow the rules, you will be punished according to the school regulations.

ZH: 这位运动员因服用兴奋剂而被取消比赛资格。
EN: The athlete was disqualified from the competition for using performance-enhancing drugs.

ZH: 这位运动员接受了赛前违规行为的处罚。
EN: The athlete received punishment for pre-competition misconduct.

ZH: 这家公司违反了劳工法规，被处以巨额罚款。
EN: The company was fined a huge amount for violating labor regulations.

ZH: 我们应该建立严格的法律制度来惩罚犯罪行为。
EN: We should establish a strict legal system to punish criminal activities.

ZH: 这个地区的交通违法行为受到了更严厉的处罚制度。
EN: The region has implemented a stricter punishment system for traffic violations.

ZH: 他对自己的错误感到非常后悔，希望不再受到任何处罚。
EN: He deeply regrets his mistakes and hopes to avoid any further punishment.

ZH: 如果你继续做出这种违法行为，你将会面临更加严重的处罚。
EN: If you continue to engage in such illegal activities, you will face more severe punishment.

ZH: 作为公民，我们应该遵守法律，并接受法律的处罚。
EN: As citizens, we should obey the law and accept the punishment if we break it.

ZH: 他因涉嫌腐败被逮捕后，将接受司法程序的处罚。
EN: After being arrested on charges of corruption, he will face the punishment of the judicial process.

ZH: 这位运动员因故意侵犯他人在赛中动作的规定而受到处罚。
EN: The athlete was penalized for intentionally violating the regulations regarding actions against opponents during the game.

ZH: 这位学生因在考试中作弊而受到了严厉的处罚。
EN: The student received severe punishment for cheating in the exam.

ZH: 每个人都应该为自己的行为负责，并承担由此带来的处罚。
EN: Everyone should be responsible for their actions and face the consequences that come with them.
